    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and polished to perfection. Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single blemish to be found\u2014it's basically brand new. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to fall in love the moment you sit inside! \u2728",
